summary: This mod basically extends the existing walls to further surround Riverwood, and add some extra protection.
descriptionHtml:
This is a complete overhaul of my previous mod, Riverwood Added Walls.

This mod basically extends the existing walls to further surround Riverwood, and add some extra protection. With this version I have left the original Riverwood area completely unaltered maintaining the rustic feel it should have.

This mod is still a work in progress and I plan to cover all of Riverwood, without modifying the area too much.
author: Omnibruce
